##Method SkImageInfo imageInfo() const #imageInfo

##Doxygen
Return ImageInfo for this canvas. If the canvas is not backed by a device
then return the result of #ImageInfo empty constructor#.
##Doxygen ##

##Example
    SkCanvas canvas;
    SkImageInfo canvasInfo = canvas.imageInfo();
    SkImageInfo emptyInfo;
    SkASSERT(emptyInfo == canvasInfo);
